metadata.name: Checks - Ape Edition
metadata.description:
A depiction of one of the most prominent symbols of our web3 community using Jack Butcher's "Checks" design.

Butcher uses Checks to simultaneously symbolize notoriety and lack thereof; people either understand web3 culture or don't, making Yuga's Apes both incredibly notable or not notable at all, depending on who the question is posed to.

Is this NFT notable? Maybe, but WTF is an NFT anyway?
